technology works Our technology uses a cooling process called subcooled nucleate This is the cooling process used in nuclear reactors, by which our tank design is ferveret technology – Subcooled boiling Ferveret technology reduces the chip temperature by a factor 2 enabling more powerful (~2X) CPUs and How our technology is different than our competitors? There are many companies in the immersion cooling Their technology is either based on single phase immersion cooling or two phase immersion Each company tries to make the case that one is better than the other At Ferveret, we understand pro and cons of both techniques, so our technology combines We take advantages of their pros, and eliminate the cons Subcooled nucleate boiling allows removing exceptionally high heat fluxes from processors or other heat generating While we take advantage of the phase change (i.e., boiling) on top of the heat source, everything looks like a single phase immersion cooling solution from With our solution there is no vapor plenum on top of our tank, which helps reducing fluid losses significantly compared to conventional two phase immersion Home

Privacy Policy – Equa Health Skip to content Privacy Policy Equa Health, Effective July , Equa Health, (“ we ”, “us” and “ our ”) cares about your privacy and wants you to be familiar with how we collect, use, and disclose your information (collectively, “ you ” and “ your ”). This Privacy Policy (“ Policy ”) describes our information practices related to information collected by us or our service providers through this website and related blogs and mobile applications (collectively, the “ Site ”). This Policy contains important information that impacts our use of your Personal Information (as described below). Please read this Policy Use of the Site and Services is absolutely conditioned upon you agreeing to our Terms of Use and to all of the information, disclosures and disclaimers contained in this From time to time, we may modify our practices that relate to our use of your Personal In such an event, we will update this Your continued use of the Site following the publication of any such revised Policy to this Site shall constitute your consent to the revised Personal Information and your Privacy As used in this Policy, “ Personal Information ” includes one or more of the following types of information: payment information (credit and or debit card numbers, ), name, title, email address, account numbers, physical address, zip code, mobile phone numbers, phone numbers, answers to questionnaires, or other such submissions or content generated by you in connection with the Site, and similar unique, personal information that could identify We do not consider “Personal Information” to include information that has been made anonymous so that it does not identify a specific Nor do we consider general information such as your geographic location, age group, gender, product and or wellness concerns when you voluntarily provide such information to us, as “Personal Information,” when not combined with information that can be used to personally identify you or any other We may receive Personal Information from third parties with whom we have a relationship or otherwise contract with to obtain such Disclosures Use of Information We may use the information that we obtain about you in the following Identifying Information . Unique identifiers (such as address(es)) are collected and may be used to respond directly to you when you request information or a response from us, as well as for verification Information You Provide to Us . We may collect and store any information you provide when you use the Site or For example, when you decide to complete a registration form or application for Services, complete an online survey or testimonial, you may be asked to provide certain information such as your contact information (name, email address, mailing address and telephone number). By communicating with us, you acknowledge that your communication may be overheard, monitored, documented, or recorded without further notice or Once you are a registered user, information is stored in your account—such as your Please note that if you choose to share information about yourself in an open format, including verbal or written testimonials, our blog or through a Site such as Facebook or Twitter, we may consider some of that information to be public information—and not Personal Payment Card Information . We use your information to process your donations to us, including, without limitation, by providing such information to third party payment Data and Data Analytics . We track the kinds of activities that you perform, profiles and questionnaires that you create and respond to, and any other information generated by you in connection with the services performed by the Sharing Information with Third We may share your information with our service providers to use in performing the Services and in performing services related to the administration, use, operation and or maintenance of our Site and or reacting to your specific Specifically, we may use third parties to facilitate our operations, customer relationship management, hosting the Site and or our online services, to send out email updates about Equa, and or to provide In connection with these offerings and operations, our service providers may have access to your Personal Information for use in connection with these business In general, the providers used by us will only collect, use and disclose your information to the extent necessary to allow them to perform the services they provide to We may also share your information as we deem necessary (i) in the event (or partial event) of a corporate sale (asset or stock), merger, reorganization, change in corporate control, acquisition, insolvency, bankruptcy or similar event, (ii) to comply with applicable law or reasonable request based upon governmental regulation, court order, subpoena or similar related action or (iii) to protect the rights, property or safety of us, our customers, our associates or others, to prevent harm or loss,

designed to meet your power needs both inside and outside your The Mango Power Union can be used as a backup home power supply and as storage for the green energy your house generates, whether it’s from solar, wind, or other renewable The Union’s detachable module, the Power Move, is a battery that gives you more than enough energy for anything you want to do The system’s advanced settings feature enables ful customization so you can tailor it to your needs, whatever they Seamless Backup The moment the grid goes down, the Mango Power Union’s stored energy starts power flowing through your Its smart switch flips on automatically so there is no electrical disruption for your important appliances, and its kWh battery capacity is designed to power essential circuits for up to 3 days emergency usage for a normal For a comprehensive list of appliances normally connected to your home’s essential circuits, click Economical Home The Mango Power Union’s Economical Mode prioritizes energy from green sources – solar, wind, or any other renewables – to guarantee a larger share of your energy consumption comes from environmentally conscious In this mode, energy generated by your solar panels (whether roof solar system or portable solar panels) in the daytime is stored and can then be used at night to help minimize total energy costs and shrink your carbon footprint in daily Control If your utility offers rates, you can charge the Mango Power Union with electricity and consume it during peak hours, so you always enjoy the lowest possible power costs and save on your energy bill every Power Supply for Living With the Mango Power Union’s detachable Power Move module, you can take power with you wherever you This kWh 2 kW battery can be used to power your electric grill, portable refrigerator, fan, air mattress inflator, or any other outdoor Monitoring and Remote Control The Mango Power Union includes an app (more about the Mango Power App in Section 4) that Chris Petersen — RADICL Defense Meet the Team Blog Careers About Our Investors Contact Us Chris Petersen CEO CTO About: Chris began his career as a consultant for Price Waterhouse (PwC) and Ernst & Young (EY) where he served Fortune customers and developed innovative software products that accelerated and differentiated their service Chris later joined Counterpane Internet Security, a pioneering managed security services provider (MSSP). At Counterpane, he built and led their threat intelligence team and was a principal contributor in the design and development of the systems, technologies, and processes that supported their security operations After Counterpane, Chris joined Enterasys Networks in a product leadership role for the Dragon Intrusion Detection System (IDS). In , Chris LogRhythm, a leader in next generation Security Information & Event Management (SIEM). As LogRhythm’s Chief Technology Officer, Chris led the vision and design of the LogRhythm platform and product He also served as Chairman, Chief Product Officer, and SVP of Customer Through his leadership, LogRhythm pioneered and drove industry advancements in SIEM, Security Orchestration Automation & Response (SOAR), User Entity Behavior Analytics (UEBA), Network Detection & Response (NDR), and Extended Detection & Response (XDR). LogRhythm earned the top spot in the Forrester Wave report for Security Analytics and has been consistent leader in the Gartner Magic Quadrant for Today, the LogRhythm platform is used by over enterprise customers, government agencies, and managed security service providers across the globe in support of their security operations Chris is an EY Entrepreneur of the year and a expert in cyber He has authored numerous whitepapers and articles in the field of cyber security and holds multiple Chris has spoken at conferences across the globe and was a faculty member at the Institute for Applied Network Chris holds a in Accounting from Colorado State University and is an active supporter of CSU’s Institute for Entrepreneurship and their Hacking for Defense (H4D) Chris lives in Boulder, Colorado where he enjoys an active life full of sports and adventure with his wife Elizabeth and their three Why I founded RADICL Defense As a cybersecurity industry veteran and inventor, I am dissatisfied with the current state of technology and the offerings available to small businesses – especially those targeted by nation state I am RADICL to defend these innovate and important companies, and by so doing, serve and defend the interests of the United We secure small and medium sized businesses from nation state level Contact info Boulder, Colorado Additional links Careers Cardinal Protocol Home Twitter App Docs Identity Issue, Manage, & Verify Programmed NFTs Cardinal is a Solana Protocol that enhances the utility of NFTs by allowing Minters Holders to issue them to beneficiaries with intrinsic caveats governing the receipt & ownership Conditional Ownership The Cardinal Protocol offers an array of parameters that issuers can combine in any number of ways to customize the nature of their beneficiary s ownership Manual Revocation An issuer may specify a manual revocation authority that can revoke the token from a beneficiary at any Upon being revoked, the token is withdrawn from the beneficiary s wallet and deposited into the issuer s Expiry An issuer may specify a expiry such that after a certain period of time, the token will be programmatically revoked from the beneficiaryâs wallet and returned to the issuer Expiry An issuer may specify a expiry such that after a beneficiary has used the token a certain number of times, it will be programmatically revoked from their wallet and returned to the issuer Bespoke Expiry In the future, an issuer will be able specify an expiry trigger tied data fed in by an For example, a token could expire be revoked based on the outcome of a sporting event or the result of an election Selective Transferability An issuer may specify that the token is selectively transferable and can thus only be traded via a permissioned transfer method intrinsic to the Cardinal Protocol An issuer may specify that the token issued is completely non tradeable such that the beneficiary would be unable to trade it via basic SPL token transfer or any cardinal specific transfer permissioned transfer Blockchain Gaming Empower gaming items and economies Blockchain gaming platforms can use the protocol to issue Cloud We re here for Contact us 7 days a week for advice on anything and The best way to get contact us is via We’re happy to assist you in any way we Frequently Asked Questions What is a reverse osmosis water filter? + Using concentrated pressure, water is pushed through an RO (reverse osmosis) membrane: a , compact membrane that even heavy metals, pesticides and volatile organic compounds (VOCs) can’t slip Heck, even fluoride and lead are out of They all have a ticket to the waste A reverse osmosis system can remove up to % of the contaminants found in tap Some RO units, like Cloud RO, even add essential trace minerals back into the When it’s all said and done, your family can enjoy , , perfectly alkalized water every Read more about reverse osmosis here . What is alkaline water? + Simply put, alkaline water is water with a pH of 8 to Your average tap water has a pH around But when it comes to nutrition and the health benefits of drinking alkaline water, pH isn t the only piece of the Alkaline water should also contain alkalizing minerals like calcium, magnesium, sodium and These minerals help the cells produce energy, fight inflammation, and support nearly every organ in the Cloud RO produces alkaline water by running purified water through a final remineralization This process naturally raises your water s pH and adds back these trace minerals providing you with perfectly clean, perfectly alkaline drinking Read more about alkaline water here . Does Cloud RO create alkaline water? + Yes! Cloud RO raises your water’s pH to alkaline levels by adding essential trace minerals like calcium and magnesium back into the purified water before it hits your This process is called These minerals are healthy, they help your water taste better, and they help deliver the alkaline water you are looking for! Read more about the alkaline filtration process here . Does Cloud RO waste water? + Kind of, not really… well, it’s The reverse osmosis process is one of the most powerful purification processes on To answer the question, we need to take a step back to fully understand how the filter Using concentrated pressure, water is pushed through an RO (reverse osmosis) membrane: a , compact filter that even heavy metals, pesticides and volatile organic compounds (VOCs) can’t slip All of the nasty toxins are forced one way, and pure water is forced the other The dirty, toxin ridden water, also referred to as grey water, is sent packing down your drain You are left with pristine drinking So, does Cloud RO waste water? Technically yes, the ratio of dirty water to clean drinking water is about 1 This is also the reason we only recommend using the RO process for drinking and cooking water supplies and not whole house And while the dirty water is technically “waste” we would argue that grey water is unfit for human consumption Read more about the benefits of reverse osmosis here . Is Cloud RO water better than bottled water? + An emphatic YES! From a water purification process, Cloud RO and bottled water filtration are likely Most bottled water manufacturers use reverse osmosis just like we BUT bottled water lacks the regulation needed to ensure you and your family aren’t consuming harmful Multiple studies have found that bottled water contains heightened levels of PFAs, microplastics, and even Furthermore, plastic leaching can introduce harmful BPAs after the water has been bottled and sits in the container for days, months or Last, but certainly not least bottled water is causing an environmental Over 1 million bottles of waters are purchased every single minute, and % of those are not So, for yourself, for your family, and for the planet earth, stop buying bottled water and start Read more about bottled water toxicity here . Can I install this myself, or does a plumber need to install it? + If you are a handy DIYer then yes, you can certainly install Cloud RO The process is straightforward and we provided detailed video With all plumbing related installations however, the risk of flooding is always a We encourage you to check out our $150 white glove installation One flat rate and you can book the install directly through our site with your With a click of a button, a Cloud certified technician shows up and gets the job Easy Whichever option you choose, rest assured that our Cloud Customer Happiness Team is always here to How does your white glove installation work? + Cloud s white glove service takes the guesswork out of your Cloud RO While self install is an option, we encourage our customers to leverage the expertise of a licensed and certified installation So how does it work? It s simple, just click to add white glove installation in your cart, complete checkout, and select a convenient date and time on the order confirmation That s it! Immunotherapy Universal Vaccine Kids Cancer Team News Investors About Us Contact Us Developing a Breakthrough Universal Cancer Vaccine The Problem Conventional cancer immunotherapy is based on finding protein marker s or mechanism s that are naturally expressed in cancer cells and then developing custom antibodies or immune cells to target those specific protein marker s for cell The main challenge with this approach is that human biology is not very predictable , and the natural protein marker s often appear in healthy normal cells as well can c er cells . As a result, any treatment targeting those natural markers may also affect normal It is only through extensive human clinical trials , on a treatment by treatment basis, that one can determine if a particular treatment is The Solution We turned this problem on its head and asked, “What if we can engineer a single occurring protein marker for all cancer cells to express, and then vaccinate against that?” We will teach the immune system what cancer cells look like, so they can be identified and By leverag ing CRISPR and mRNA technologies, we are on a quest to develop a breakthrough a Universal Cancer Vaccine to do just We filed a U . S . provisional patent application in .
